original_title: Cuomo denies counting on Trump for NYC mayor race, despite new report | Fox News
article_summary: New York City mayoral candidates Andrew Cuomo and Curtis Sliwa trade barbs, with Cuomo denying reports of a potential Trump endorsement, while Sliwa criticizes Cuomo's policies and ties him to Trump. Both candidates are distancing themselves from Trump's involvement in the race, with Sliwa stating it wouldn't be helpful for Trump to intervene.</s>
